<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٦٠٥٩ - حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ فُضَيْلٍ، عَنِ ابْنِ شُبْرُمَةَ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ الْحَسَنَ،<span class="c5"> يَتَمَثَّلُ هَذَا الْبَيْتَ:</span> <span class="c2">«<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
